Beauty of Joseon 
Rice and probiotics sunscreen 

ingrediënt: Reliëf sun Aqua Fresh Rice +B5 vitamin 
 SPF 50+

packaging: its nice and the top is made plastic, and the Bottom is aluminium.but it have a nice feel and its sturdy in my hand nothing bad to say.

My Opinion: im a dry /sensitive/ sometimes acne prone skin girl. And for the first time in my live i really like to wear a SPF without any problems, not a White cast, no problems for my skin, no acne, no rash, no redness, no stingy feeling. It absorbs perfectly in the skin 

It does not make me more oily then a normal day or when i should not wear the SPF. So its normal. Also the smell is nice not overwhelmed just a nice, Soft little smell to it.The feeling on my skin is nice and soft also. Honestly if you have sensitive skin/oily/acne prone i can comfirm you, you will love this sunscreen.
